==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: blastodisc
<hw>blastodisc</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a disc-shaped layer of cells on
the surface of the yolk mass of an egg (such as that of a bird) which
develops to form the embryo.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> germinal disc, germinal area.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

